title: Osho_Dance your way to God_V.Khanna
description:
"Dance your Way to god".This video was created by known Indian actor Vinod Khanna and it was dedicated to Osho and celebration of His birthday. Vinod Khanna was living with Osho in Rajneeshpuram as his the gardener and the devotee.
It is a mixture of Osho talks in Hindi and English, with devotional songs.
Some well known persons of India are telling their impressions about Osho.
Hindi language was translated to English by Dharma Karim and Prashant Singh.
For correct English, thanks to Tosho Bailey. Video was removed from Youtube, and it is not allowed to share in public becaus e of OIF's claiming copyright on Osho and His name. Please share it in private
